{"tid":1612909,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論］打狗棒","createTime":"2019-10-02T11:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T11:40:58.000Z","uid":11081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cb47e7b4a72e33de806bfe3eacf58961b687c7d1","tid":1612909,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcToPKoowGepUeyvp2fu5YjVN15S9Tl8r91gj1w8gAN8o6MM5r66\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcToPKoowGepUeyvp2fu5YjVN15S9Tl8r91gj1w8gAN8o6MM5r66&h=88f8afc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打狗棒法乃金庸武俠小說體系中絕頂的武功之一， 堪稱天下第一下棒法，威力雖不及降龍十八掌，但每招都是變幻茣測， 連西毒歐陽鋒也要花幾天時間才能拆解，而其靈蛇杖法亦不敵，足見其厲害 因此亦可發揮很巨大的威力，連五絕也忌彈三分。是丐幫幫主代代相傳的兩大謢幫神功之一。因為乞丐在街上討飯，經常會受家犬或野狗襲擊，所以丐幫人物出外行乞時，手中多執一根竹棒防身。打狗棒法的特點是靈活躍動，機變百出，正是由與狗搏鬥的實際生活體驗中發展出來的技巧<br />\n<br />\n由於打狗棒失傳多時，導致犬隻肆無忌憚亂咬人<br />\n擾亂社會，不少中原義士受到犬畜襲擊<br />\n望各中原義士一齊尋回打狗棒，擊退犬畜<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以暴制亂</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續..."},{"pid":"23ec18c9af9ab037db851e53ce21b8ec1f919f84","tid":1612909,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cd4b549d03fec7592d3f7f2ff54e5851fa7307","tid":1612909,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22785f8b7e9a29a3746dd6861b232c860320e30a","tid":1612909,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}